```

Both subclasses only override `getSourcepath()`, `doFinish()`, and `getDependencyScope()`. This means the PR's restructuring of `doCompile()` (wrapping legacy logic in an `else` block) will affect both compile and test-compile goals identically, which is the intended behavior.

